<item>
            <title>[LU-8195] sanityn test_77f: failed to operate on TBF rules</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8195</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for John Hammond &amp;lt;john.hammond@intel.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/32b35dee-2106-11e6-9089-5254006e85c2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.hpdd.intel.com/test_sets/32b35dee-2106-11e6-9089-5254006e85c2&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sub-test test_77f failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;failed to operate on TBF rules
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Somehow an extra space gets in to the value string:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;CMD: trevis-18vm3 lctl set_param ost.OSS.ost_io.nrs_tbf_rule=start\ runas\ {iozone.500\  dd.500\ tiotest.500}\ 1000
trevis-18vm3: error: set_param: setting /proc/fs/lustre/ost/OSS/ost_io/nrs_tbf_rule=start runas {iozone.500 : Invalid argument
trevis-18vm3: error: set_param: setting dd.500 tiotest.500} 1000=: Invalid argument
ost.OSS.ost_io.nrs_tbf_rule=start runas {iozone.500 
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Info required for matching: sanityn 77f&lt;/p&gt;</description>
